# ğŸ¯ Virtual Keyboard with Hand Tracking

## ğŸ“ Description
The **Virtual Keyboard with Hand Tracking** is an innovative touchless typing solution that combines computer vision and artificial intelligence to enable users to type using hand gestures. Built with **Python**, **MediaPipe**, **OpenCV**, and **Pygame**, this application provides a modern, accessible way to interact with digital interfaces without physical contact.

The system uses advanced hand tracking technology to detect finger movements and translates them into keyboard input, making it perfect for environments where hygiene is crucial, accessibility is needed, or traditional input methods are not available.

## ğŸš€ Features

* ğŸ‘‹ **Advanced Hand Tracking** - Uses Google's MediaPipe to detect and track 21 key points on each hand with high precision
* âŒ¨ï¸ **Virtual QWERTY Keyboard** - Full keyboard layout with responsive key design and visual feedback
* ğŸŒ **Bilingual Support** - Seamless switching between English and Arabic layouts with proper RTL text rendering
* ğŸ¯ **Smart Key Selection** - Point with your index finger to select keys with a 1-second hold-to-press mechanism
* âœŒï¸ **Gesture Controls** - Use victory sign (peace sign) with both hands to switch between language layouts
* â±ï¸ **Visual Feedback** - Progress bars and color-coded indicators show selection and press progress
* ğŸ¨ **Modern UI Design** - Beautiful gradient backgrounds, rounded corners, and smooth animations
* ğŸ“± **Responsive Interface** - Supports both fullscreen and windowed modes with dynamic scaling
* ğŸ“¹ **Live Camera Feed** - Real-time camera preview with hand landmark visualization
* ğŸ”¤ **Arabic Text Processing** - Proper Arabic character shaping and bidirectional text support
* ğŸ® **Smooth Performance** - Optimized for 60 FPS with efficient rendering

